snippet.title: Horizon Forbidden West - Gameplay Trailer | Game Awards 2021
snippet.description:
We got another look at Horizon Forbidden West, showcasing a number of Aloy's different outfits that she'll be able to equip throughout her adventure. Revealed at The Game Awards 2021

#IGN #Gaming #GameAwards2021
